  "prompt": "What is the best coffee at Starbucks USA?",
  "response": "The \"best\" coffee at Starbucks can be subjective, as it depends on personal taste preferences. However, here are some of the most popular and highly recommended options in the U.S.:\n\n### 1. **Pumpkin Spice Latte (Seasonal)**  \n   A fall favorite, this latte combines espresso, steamed milk, pumpkin spice flavoring, and whipped cream. It\u2019s a cult classic for a reason!\n\n### 2. **Caramel Macchiato**  \n   A layered drink with vanilla syrup, steamed milk, espresso, and caramel drizzle. It\u2019s sweet, creamy, and loved by many.\n\n### 3. **Caffe Mocha**  \n   A blend of espresso, steamed milk, and chocolate syrup, topped with whipped cream. Perfect for chocolate lovers.\n\n### 4. **Vanilla Sweet Cream Cold Brew**  \n   A smooth cold brew coffee topped with a splash of vanilla sweet cream. It\u2019s refreshing and slightly sweet.\n\n### 5. **Nitro Cold Brew**  \n   A velvety, nitrogen-infused cold brew that\u2019s smooth and creamy without added milk or sugar. Great for purists who love strong coffee.\n\n### 6. **Flat White**  \n   A stronger, creamier espresso drink made with ristretto shots and velvety steamed milk. Ideal for those who enjoy a bolder coffee flavor.\n\n### 7. **Iced White Chocolate Mocha**  \n   A decadent iced option with espresso, white chocolate sauce, milk, and whipped cream. Perfect for a sweet treat.\n\n### 8. **Honey Almondmilk Flat White (Customizable)**  \n   A dairy-free option made with almond milk, espresso, and a touch of honey. It\u2019s smooth and slightly sweet.\n\n### Pro Tip:  \nIf you\u2019re unsure what to order, ask the barista for their recommendation or customize your drink to suit your taste. Starbucks offers endless options for personalization!\n\nWhat\u2019s your go-to Starbucks drink?",
  "temperature": 1.0,
